room_title: Escape room "Pandora's Box" by Hour To Exit in New York
room_description: Curiosity killed the Kingdom... or did it? Pandora has opened the box that Zeus has strictly forbidden. Releasing all the evil spirits upon humanity. Her curious ways just might ruin the Kingdom that Zeus so dearly loves. She has enlisted your help. Can you bravely shut the box or will your curiosity leave you stuck forever?
